2218
01:42:16,140 --> 01:42:21,140
of the tissue that it's interfacing with,

2219
01:42:21,600 --> 01:42:24,329
and then it just amplitude modulates

2220
01:42:24,329 --> 01:42:27,210
the wavefront that comes
back to the source.

2221
01:42:27,210 --> 01:42:29,819
