2225
01:42:37,529 --> 01:42:40,139
to get that recording, amplifying it,

2226
01:42:40,140 --> 01:42:42,570
and then just modulating.

2227
01:42:42,569 --> 01:42:46,039
And the mechanism that you can enable that

2228
01:42:46,039 --> 01:42:48,269
