energy and vice versa.

2231
01:42:55,470 --> 01:42:58,170
So you can kind of have this interplay

2232
01:42:58,170 --> 01:42:59,970
between the ultrasonic domain

2233
01:42:59,970 --> 01:43:02,972
and electrical domain that
is the biological tissue.

2234
