04:20:20,760 --> 04:20:23,159
after exposing the brain and
presenting it to the robot

5476
04:20:23,159 --> 04:20:28,159
and placed the targets on the robot

5477
04:20:29,879 --> 04:20:32,189
software interface that tells the robot

5478
04:20:32,190 --> 04:20:35,470
where it's going to insert
each thread that was done

5479
04:20:36,420 --> 04:20:39,899
with my hand on the mouse,
