6562
05:12:50,819 --> 05:12:53,310
of the local field potential

6563
05:12:53,310 --> 05:12:55,470
or the, yeah, the voltage essentially

6564
05:12:55,470 --> 05:12:57,090
measured by that electrode.

6565
05:12:57,090 --> 05:12:59,670
And we have a certain
mode in our application

6566
05:12:59,669 --> 05:13:02,039
