put it in front of him.

6662
05:16:30,689 --> 05:16:33,329
And we said, "Hey, you
tell us what's going on.

6663
05:16:33,330 --> 05:16:34,163
We're not you.

6664
05:16:34,163 --> 05:16:36,209
You're able to imagine different things,

6665
05:16:36,209 --> 05:16:38,099
and we know that it's
modulating some of these neurons

6666
05:16:38,099 --> 05:16:39,659
so you figure out for us

6667
05:16:39,659 --> 05:16:41,669
what that is actually representing."

6668
05:16:41,669 --> 05:16:43,109
And so he played with it for a bit.

6669
05:16:43,110 --> 05:16:44,850
He was like, "I don't quite get it yet."

6670
05:16:44,849 --> 05:16:46,169
He played for a bit longer.

6671
05:16:46,169 --> 05:16:49,079
