6688
05:17:23,544 --> 05:17:24,903
- 1,024, yeah.

6689
05:17:25,776 --> 05:17:28,280
- That's incredible that that works.

6690
05:17:28,279 --> 05:17:32,592
When I was learning about all
this and like loading it in,

6691
05:17:33,630 --> 05:17:36,299
