6765
05:20:26,400 --> 05:20:29,760
And so the number of neurons
that you're gonna pick up

6766
05:20:29,759 --> 05:20:30,959
with any given electrode

6767
05:20:30,959 --> 05:20:33,659
is just a small radius
around that electrode.

6768
05:20:33,659 --> 05:20:35,340
And the other thing worth understanding

6769
05:20:35,340 --> 05:20:36,470
about the underlying biology here

6770
05:20:36,470 --> 05:20:38,610
is that when neurons
produce an action potential,

6771
05:20:38,610 --> 05:20:41,520
