6774
05:20:46,950 --> 05:20:50,069
of a neuron firing is
one millisecond wide.

6775
05:20:50,069 --> 05:20:52,829
And if you want to detect
that an individual spike

6776
05:20:52,830 --> 05:20:55,770
is occurring or not, you
need to sample that signal

6777
05:20:55,770 --> 05:20:58,500
or sample the local full
potential nearby that neuron

6778
05:20:58,500 --> 05:20:59,909
much more frequently
than once a millisecond.

6779
05:20:59,909 --> 05:21:02,759
You need to sample many,
