6780
05:21:02,759 --> 05:21:04,619
to be able to detect that this is actually

6781
05:21:04,619 --> 05:21:05,819
the characteristic waveform

6782
05:21:05,819 --> 05:21:07,676
of a neuron producing an action potential.

6783
05:21:07,676 --> 05:21:11,279
And so we sample across
