8727
06:31:15,330 --> 06:31:16,830
that there's temporal codes.

8728
06:31:16,830 --> 06:31:20,100
So timing codes of like exactly
when particular neurons fire

8729
06:31:20,099 --> 06:31:24,029
is the mechanism of
information representation.

