representing information

8735
06:31:33,630 --> 06:31:37,860
by changing the sort of
frequency of a neuron firing,

8736
06:31:37,860 --> 06:31:39,659
what really matters is sort of the delta

8737
06:31:39,659 --> 06:31:41,546
between sort of the
baseline state of the neuron

8738
06:31:41,546 --> 06:31:43,709
and what it looks like
when it's modulated.

8739
06:31:43,709 --> 06:31:45,930
And what we've observed and
what has also been observed

8740
06:31:45,930 --> 06:31:47,939
in academic work is
that that baseline rate,

8741
06:31:47,939 --> 06:31:49,559
sort of the, if you're
to target the scale,

8742
06:31:49,560 --> 06:31:53,010
if you imagine that
analogy for like measuring

8743
06:31:53,009 --> 06:31:54,629
flour or something when you're baking,

8744
06:31:54,630 --> 06:31:57,180
that baseline state of
