8752
06:32:11,310 --> 06:32:12,990
is what's causing this downstream bias.

8753
06:32:12,990 --> 06:32:13,890
There can be other effects,

8754
06:32:13,889 --> 06:32:15,029
non-linear effects on top of that,

8755
06:32:15,029 --> 06:32:16,289
but at least, at a very first order

8756
06:32:16,290 --> 06:32:17,610
description of the problem,

8757
06:32:17,610 --> 06:32:18,875
that's what we observe day to day

8758
06:32:18,875 --> 06:32:20,909
is that the baseline firing
rate of any particular

8759
06:32:20,909 --> 06:32:23,610
neuron are observed on a
particular channel is changing.

