9179
06:47:37,740 --> 06:47:39,730
And so I think I'm very aligned with

9180
06:47:42,060 --> 06:47:44,940
sort of "The Hitchhiker's
Guide to the Galaxy" version

9181
06:47:44,939 --> 06:47:46,139
of this question, which is basically,

9182
06:47:46,139 --> 06:47:48,212
if we can ask the right questions,

9183
06:47:49,349 --> 06:47:50,549
it's much more likely we find

9184
06:47:50,549 --> 06:47:52,349
the meaning of human existence.

9185
06:47:52,349 --> 06:47:53,182
And so in the short term,

9186
06:47:53,183 --> 06:47:56,340
as a heuristic in the sort
of search policy space,

9187
06:47:56,340 --> 06:47:58,380
we should try to increase the diversity

9188
06:47:58,380 --> 06:48:00,780
of people asking such questions,

9189
06:48:00,779 --> 06:48:02,189
or generally of consciousness

9190
06:48:02,189 --> 06:48:04,340
and conscious beings
asking such questions.

9191
06:48:05,220 --> 06:48:07,950
So again, I think I'll take
the 'I don't know card' here,

9192
06:48:07,950 --> 06:48:10,530
but say I do think there are
meaningful things we can do

9193
06:48:10,529 --> 06:48:13,199
that improve the likelihood
of answering that question.

9194
06:48:13,200 --> 06:48:16,470
- It's interesting how
much value you assign

9195
06:48:16,470 --> 06:48:18,663
to the task of asking the right questions.

9196
06:48:19,557 --> 06:48:23,250
That's the main thing is not the answers,

9197
06:48:23,250 --> 06:48:24,720
it's the questions.

9198
06:48:24,720 --> 06:48:26,620
- This point by the way is driven home

9199
06:48:27,900 --> 06:48:29,610
in a very painful way when
