mean, if they're firing now,

9716
07:11:49,049 --> 07:11:51,299
let's see if I can
affect them in some way."

9717
07:11:51,299 --> 07:11:53,790
So I started trying to
like wiggle my fingers

9718
07:11:53,790 --> 07:11:56,909
