9724
07:12:08,819 --> 07:12:10,200
And I was like, "Oh, that's cool."

9725
07:12:10,200 --> 07:12:11,197
And everyone around me was just like,

9726
07:12:11,197 --> 07:12:12,220
"Well, what are you seeing?"

9727
07:12:12,220 --> 07:12:14,639
I was like, "Look, look at this one.

9728
07:12:14,639 --> 07:12:18,389
Look at like this top row, third
box over this yellow spike.

9729
07:12:18,389 --> 07:12:21,540
Like that's me right there, there, there."

9730
07:12:21,540 --> 07:12:23,250
And everyone was freaking out.

9731
07:12:23,250 --> 07:12:24,569
They started like clapping.

9732
07:12:24,569 --> 07:12:27,299
I was like, "That's super unnecessary."

9733
07:12:27,299 --> 07:12:28,132
- That's awesome.
- This is what's

9734
07:12:28,133 --> 07:12:29,760
