9740
07:12:42,659 --> 07:12:44,040
to see if anything would happen.

9741
07:12:44,040 --> 07:12:47,549
There was a lot of other things going on,

9742
07:12:47,549 --> 07:12:50,579
but that big yellow spike was
the one that stood out to me.

9743
07:12:50,580 --> 07:12:54,180
Like I'm sure that if I would've
stared at it long enough,

9744
07:12:54,180 --> 07:12:57,750
I could have mapped out
maybe 100 different things.

9745
07:12:57,750 --> 07:13:00,360
But the big yellow spike
