9771
07:14:04,169 --> 07:14:08,699
I can, if I try enough,

9772
07:14:08,700 --> 07:14:10,799
I can wiggle some of my fingers.

9773
07:14:10,799 --> 07:14:12,869
Not like on command.

9774
07:14:12,869 --> 07:14:15,119
It's more like if I try to move,

9775
07:14:15,119 --> 07:14:18,329
say my right pinky and I
