9776
07:14:18,330 --> 07:14:20,430
after a few seconds, it'll wiggle.

9777
07:14:20,430 --> 07:14:21,959
So I know there's stuff there.

9778
07:14:21,959 --> 07:14:24,456
Like I know, and that happens with a few

9779
07:14:24,456 --> 07:14:26,402
- -different of my fingers and stuff.

9780
07:14:28,229 --> 07:14:30,329
But yeah, that's what they tell you to do.

9781
07:14:31,349 --> 07:14:33,209
One of the people at the time

9782
07:14:33,209 --> 07:14:35,430
when I was in the hospital
came in and told me,

9783
07:14:35,430 --> 07:14:39,630
for one guy who had recovered
