9784
07:14:39,630 --> 07:14:43,200
what he thought about every
day was actually walking,

9785
07:14:43,200 --> 07:14:46,650
like the act of walking
just over and over again.

9786
07:14:46,650 --> 07:14:48,659
So I tried that for years.

9787
07:14:48,659 --> 07:14:53,659
I tried just imagining
walking, which it's hard.

9788
07:14:54,000 --> 07:14:59,000
It's hard to imagine like all
of the steps that go into,

9789
07:15:00,060 --> 07:15:01,170
well, taking a step,

9790
07:15:01,169 --> 07:15:03,029
like all of the things that have to move,

9791
07:15:03,029 --> 07:15:06,569
like all of the activations
that have to happen

9792
07:15:06,569 --> 07:15:09,750
along your leg in order
for one step to occur.

9793
07:15:09,750 --> 07:15:11,340
- But you're not just imagining.

9794
07:15:11,340 --> 07:15:12,930
You're like doing it, right?

9795
07:15:12,930 --> 07:15:13,979
- I'm trying, yeah.

9796
07:15:13,979 --> 07:15:18,979
So it's like, it's imagining over again

9797
07:15:19,439 --> 07:15:21,869
what I had to do to take a step,

9798
07:15:21,869 --> 07:15:24,479
because it's not something
any of us think about.

9799
07:15:24,479 --> 07:15:26,819
You wanna walk and you take a step.

9800
07:15:26,819 --> 07:15:28,860
You don't think about all
of the different things

9801
07:15:28,860 --> 07:15:31,200
that are going on in your body.

9802
07:15:31,200 --> 07:15:34,947
So I had to recreate that in
my head as much as I could.

9803
07:15:34,947 --> 07:15:37,650
And then I practice it
over and over and over.

9804
07:15:37,650 --> 07:15:39,569
- So it's not like a
third person perspective.

9805
07:15:39,569 --> 07:15:41,159
It's a first person perspective.

9806
07:15:41,159 --> 07:15:42,389
You're like, it's not like

