07:15:42,389 --> 07:15:44,399
you're imagining yourself walking.

9808
07:15:44,400 --> 07:15:47,730
You're like literally
doing this, everything,

9809
07:15:47,729 --> 07:15:49,380
all the same stuff as if you're walking.

9810
07:15:49,380 --> 07:15:51,870
- Yeah, which was hard.

9811
07:15:51,869 --> 07:15:53,489
It was hard at the beginning.

9812
07:15:53,490 --> 07:15:54,630
- Like frustrating hard,

9813
07:15:54,630 --> 07:15:56,639
or like actually cognitively hard?

9814
07:15:56,639 --> 07:15:58,622
Like which way?
