drug that was in her system.

9818
07:16:12,689 --> 07:16:14,909
And then she like finds some way to get

9819
07:16:14,909 --> 07:16:17,189
into the back of a truck or something,

9820
07:16:17,189 --> 07:16:20,699
and she stares at her
toe and she says, "Move."

9821
07:16:20,700 --> 07:16:22,409
Like move your big toe.

9822
