stared at my body and said,

9826
07:16:36,906 --> 07:16:38,430
"Move your index finger.

9827
07:16:38,430 --> 07:16:39,836
Move your big toe."

9828
07:16:40,709 --> 07:16:43,079
Sometimes, vocalizing it like out loud,

9829
07:16:43,080 --> 07:16:44,370
sometimes just thinking it.

9830
07:16:44,369 --> 07:16:47,279
I tried every different way to do this

9831
07:16:47,279 --> 07:16:49,289
to try to get some movement back.

9832
07:16:49,290 --> 07:16:54,290
And it's hard because it
actually is like taxing,

9833
07:16:54,330 --> 07:16:56,640
like physically taxing on my body,

9834
07:16:56,639 --> 07:16:58,559
which is something I
would've never expected,

9835
07:16:58,560 --> 07:17:00,150
'cause it's not like I'm moving,

9836
07:17:00,150 --> 07:17:05,150
but it feels like there's
a buildup of, I don't know,

9837
07:17:05,610 --> 07:17:10,610
the only way I can describe
