9838
07:17:10,709 --> 07:17:14,759
that aren't getting
through from my brain down,

9839
07:17:14,759 --> 07:17:17,009
'cause there's that gap in my spinal cord.

9840
07:17:17,009 --> 07:17:21,359
So brain down, and then from
my hand back up to the brain.

9841
07:17:21,360 --> 07:17:24,040
And so it feels like those signals

9842
07:17:25,080 --> 07:17:28,530
get stuck in whatever body
part that I'm trying to move.

9843
07:17:28,529 --> 07:17:30,239
And they just build up and build up

9844
07:17:30,240 --> 07:17:32,190
and build up until they burst.

9845
07:17:32,189 --> 07:17:35,639
And then once they burst, I
get like this really weird

9846
07:17:35,639 --> 07:17:38,700
sensation of everything
sort of like dissipating

9847
07:17:38,700 --> 07:17:41,073
back out to level, and then I do it again.

9848
07:17:42,599 --> 07:17:46,889
It's also just like a fatigue
